data.description: Welcome home to this Gold-Fortified townhome in the heart of Daphne!  This 3 bedroom/2.5 bath corner-unit is located close to the back entrance and has only one shared wall.  Downstairs, you will find a large living/dining area, a half-bath, attached one-car garage, and modern kitchen that includes stainless steel appliances and granite counters.  Upstairs, you will find the large primary suite, 2 bedrooms that share a full bath, and laundry off of the main hallway.  Amenities galore in this gated community incluuding pool, clubhouse, exercise room, and so much more.  The HOA also provides services such as landscaping, exterior maintenance (excluding windows and doors), insurance on the exterior, and pest control, providing you with the perks of home-ownership without many of the costs and upkeep.  This location cannot be beat as it is just minutes from shopping, dining, and schools while also providing easy access to I-10.  And as if it couldn't get any better, the seller is offering $3000 toward buyer's closing costs.  You won't want to let this one get away, so call your favorite agent today to schedule your showing!  Note: property taxes do not reflect homestead. (ANY/ALL UPDATES ARE PER SELLER). LISTING BROKER MAKES NO REPRESENTATION TO SQUARE FOOTAGE ACCURACY. BUYER TO VERIFY.
